long.am,bn,en,en_AU,en_GB,en_US,es_419,fa,fi,:
Need a free and simple method of tracking time for projects/payroll. 

Begin using this free extension to do time tracking. 

Simply write down the project title and press start
Our time tracker will begin the time.
Once you finish the project, press stop and the time tracking will stop for this project
You can start and pause projects whenever you want.

Once you have finished your time tracking, its possible to export this data out in CSV format so you can prepare the data for clients/show the time taken for each task. 

Disclaimer: Please note this extension is NOT made by Google and is made by an independent development team. All copyrights belong to their respective owners.
Google doesn’t endorse or sponsor this Chrome extension. Free Time Clock is not owned by, is not licensed by and is not a subsidiary of Google Inc.
